column3: [ geo ] of ( [ * , distance ( geo , $location . current_location ) ] of sort ( distance ( geo , $location . current_location ) asc of @org.schema.Restaurant . Restaurant ( ) filter servesCuisine =~ " هندی " ) ) [ 1 ] ;

column2: جستجوی یک رستوران چینی در LOCATION_0 با حداقل NUMBER_0 بررسی.
column3: @org.schema.Restaurant . Restaurant ( ) filter aggregateRating . reviewCount >= NUMBER_0 && geo == LOCATION_0 && servesCuisine =~ " چینی " ;

column2: رتبه بندی pizzeria uno در LOCATION_0 چقدر است؟
column3: [ aggregateRating.ratingValue ] of @org.schema.Restaurant . Restaurant ( ) filter geo == LOCATION_0 && name =~ " pizzeria uno " ;
[ aggregateRating.ratingValue ] of @org.schema.Restaurant . Restaurant ( ) filter id == null ^^org.schema.Restaurant:Restaurant ( " نوار برمودا " ) ;

column2: مکان و نام نزدیکترین رستوران مکزیکی را به من نشان دهید.
column3: [ geo ] of ( [ * , distance ( geo , $location . current_location ) ] of sort ( distance ( geo , $location . current_location ) asc of @org.schema.Restaurant . Restaurant ( ) filter servesCuisine =~ " مکزیکی " ) ) [ 1 ] ;
